text: Pasar Minggu Station (PSM) () is a railway station in Pasar Minggu, South Jakarta. It serves the KA Commuter Jabodetabek Red and Yellow Lines from Bogor/Depok to Jakarta Kota and Bogor/Depok to Jatinegara respectively. ==Services== The following is a list of train services at the Pasar Minggu Station * Commuterline ** Red Line to / and ** Yellow Line to / and ** Yellow Line () to and Category:South Jakarta Category:Railway stations in Jakarta
